name: 1741-academy-award-outline
title: Academy award
description: In my dreams, I see myself with an Academy Award for the best actress. This Lottie animation illustrates an Academy Award.

name: 1760-laurel-wreath-outline
title: Laurel
description: You might have succeeded but you can't rest on your laurels. This Lottie animation illustrates a laurel.

name: 1840-thumbleweed-outline
title: Tumbleweed
description: I don't know about you but there's something mystical about a tumbleweed rolling in the wind. This Lottie animation illustrates a tumbleweed.

name: 1862-genie-lamp-outline
title: Genie lamp
description: Most of my problems would disappear if I just found a good genie lamp. This Lottie animation illustrates a genie lamp.

name: 1864-director-chair-outline
title: Director chair
description: Maybe one day you will be sitting in a director's chair, turning your visions into cinema-ready movies. This Lottie animation illustrates a director chair.

name: 1867-genie-outline
title: Genie
description: Sing with Christina: I'm a genie in a bottle, baby... This Lottie animation illustrates a genie.

name: 1868-alien-outline
title: Alien
description: I am a legal alien: a Polish girl in Spain! This Lottie animation illustrates an alien.

name: 1871-red-carpet-outline
title: Red carpet
description: They ooze so much confidence that everywhere they walk it feels like they are on the red carpet. This Lottie animation illustrates a red carpet.

name: 1872-small-cute-monster-outline
title: Monster
description: Beware of jealousy: it is a green-eyed monster. This Lottie animation illustrates a monster.

name: 1876-cinema-outline
title: Cinema
description: I love summer air, long summer nights, and outdoor cinemas. Have you ever been to one of these? This Lottie animation illustrates a cinema.

name: 1877-spotlight-outline
title: Spotlight
description: She was nervous before her performance but she still stole the spotlight. This Lottie animation illustrates the spotlight.

name: 1879-countdown-outline
title: Countdown
description: Welcome to our spaceship. We're going to leave Earth in 3...2...1! This Lottie animation illustrates a countdown.

name: 1881-microphone-outline
title: Microphone
description: When she got her first microphone, she decided to become a professional singer. This Lottie animation illustrates a microphone.

name: 1882-anonymus-mask-outline
title: Mask
description: He said: the world's a stage and we all wear masks. This Lottie animation illustrates a mask.
